l as mentoring many of the 20th century's most influential physicists, including Werner Heisenberg, Wolfgang Pauli, and J. Robert Oppenheimer.[5](https://www.optica.org/get_involved/awards_and_honors/awards/award_award_histories/bornhistory/), [7](https://www.americanscientist.org/article/born-unto-trouble), [8](https://www.ed.ac.uk/about/people/plaques/born)"
